name: Goomba (Super Mario)
description:
Goomba is a fictional species in the Super Mario franchise. In the series they serve as an easy enemy for the player to defeat.  They have become an iconic part of the franchise appearing in most Super Mario media. 

This artwork in particular is taken from the 1985 video game Super Mario Bros for the NES. Their color palette has been modified to resemble the goomba's more modern appearance.
